Haute Couture | Fan Bingbing 范冰冰 style fashion

Hello to all my Chinese followers!

I salute those of you that reacted so kindly to my previous work. I was not able to understand your comments because I do not speak the same language as you.

However, even if we are different, we all speak the same language of beauty.

This is therefore an homage to you and to the actress 范冰冰 which has a very notable fashion sense worthy of being called "Haute Couture".

Enter my Haute Couture universe with this LoRA!
